From 74f8842efcf00c800a018a0e5591eae6ac046152 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 18:20:53 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] i_oplmusic: restore from Chocolate DOOM

Enable authentic music like it was on SB16 with OPL3 emulation.

This brings back the previously removed OPL3 music emulator
(Nuked-OPL3-fast) which renders the original synth patterns included
in the WAD files. Wired up to the SDL3 audio path. Tested, and it
sounds great.

Signed-off-by: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
