+ *          Feedback and Rhythm part calculation information.
+ *      forums.submarine.org.uk(carbon14, opl3):
+ *          Tremolo and phase generator calculation information.
+ *      OPLx decapsulated(Matthew Gambrell, Olli Niemitalo):
